@startuml
title Try-On Render/Encode
actor User
boundary WebApp
control Backend
entity RenderService
entity S3

WebApp -> Backend: POST /api/tryon/render {jobId}
Backend -> RenderService: Render + resize + encode
RenderService --> Backend: Binary kết quả
Backend -> S3: Upload CDN
S3 --> Backend: URL public/presigned
Backend --> WebApp: 200 {url}
WebApp --> User: Hiển thị ảnh đã render
@enduml

